commits.message:
Feature/target parser (#2)

* High-level test case, test parsing single class

* Minimum to pass target type test

* Add expect any iterable item passes callable

* Test, minimum for matching target reflection

* Finish hard-coded parser happy path

* Add tests and implementation with actual parsing

* Check multiple, repeatable attributes

* Make sure targets share reflections

* Add tests and implementations for propery attribute

* add support for multiple props in group

* Support repeatable property attributes

* Make sure parse attribute groups correctly

* Rename test methods to suck less

* Add support for constants

* Add support for methods

* Add support for method parameters

* Improve tests, add support for function params

* Change test case to allow multiple fixtures

* Add support for scanning multiple dirs

* Make sure we only check php files

* Support filtering attributes

* minor improvements to parser check
